<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EzFMC — Every Litre. Every Station. Total Command.</title>
    <meta name="description"
        content="EzFMC is the purpose-built ERP for Oil Marketing Companies in Ghana. NPA compliance, UPPF automation, station operations, finance, and AI intelligence — all in one platform.">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *,
        *::before,
        *::after {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box
        }

        :root {
            --bg-deepest: #06090f;
            --bg-deep: #0b1120;
            --bg-card: #111827;
            --bg-card-hover: #1a2540;
            --border: #1e293b;
            --border-glow: #334155;
            --text-dim: #64748b;
            --text-mid: #94a3b8;
            --text-light: #cbd5e1;
            --text-bright: #f1f5f9;
            --white: #fff;
            --blue: #0ea5e9;
            --blue-deep: #0369a1;
            --blue-glow: rgba(14, 165, 233, .12);
            --blue-glow-strong: rgba(14, 165, 233, .25);
            --amber: #f59e0b;
            --amber-deep: #b45309;
            --amber-glow: rgba(245, 158, 11, .10);
            --amber-glow-strong: rgba(245, 158, 11, .25);
            --green: #22c55e;
            --green-glow: rgba(34, 197, 94, .12);
            --red: #ef4444;
            --red-glow: rgba(239, 68, 68, .10);
            --font-head: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
            --font-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-body);
            background: var(--bg-deepest);
            color: var(--text-mid);
            line-height: 1.7;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 5px
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: var(--bg-deepest)
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: var(--blue-deep);
            border-radius: 3px
        }

        .ctn {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem
        }

        /* === NAV === */
        .nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            transition: all .4s ease
        }

        .nav.scrolled {
            background: rgba(6, 9, 15, .92);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: .7rem 0
        }

        .nav .ctn {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .6rem;
            text-decoration: none
        }

        .logo-mark {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--blue-deep));
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: .85rem;
            color: var(--white);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--blue-glow-strong)
        }

        .logo-name {
            font-family: var(--font-head);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--white);
            letter-spacing: -.02em
        }

        .logo-name span {
            color: var(--amber)
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            list-style: none
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--text-dim);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: .85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color .3s
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--blue)
        }

        .btn-cta {
            background: var(--blue);
            color: var(--white) !important;
            padding: .55rem 1.4rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: .82rem;
            letter-spacing: .02em;
            transition: all .3s;
            box-shadow: 0 0 16px var(--blue-glow-strong)
        }

        .btn-cta:hover {
            background: #38bdf8;
            box-shadow: 0 0 28px var(--blue-glow-strong);
            transform: translateY(-1px)
        }

        .mob-tog {
            display: none;
            background: 0;
            border: 0;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: .4rem
        }

        .mob-tog span {
            display: block;
            width: 20px;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--text-light);
            margin: 4px 0;
            transition: .3s
        }

        /* === HERO === */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            padding: 7rem 0 5rem;
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .hero-glow {
            position: absolute;
            top: -200px;
            right: -100px;
            width: 700px;
            height: 700px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--blue-glow) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none
        }

        .hero-glow2 {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -200px;
            left: -100px;
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--amber-glow) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none
        }

        .hero .ctn {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
            align-items: center
        }

        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .5rem;
            padding: .35rem 1rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: .72rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: .08em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--blue);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            background: var(--blue-glow)
        }

        .hero-badge .dot {
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            background: var(--green);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: blink 2s infinite
        }

        @keyframes blink {

            0%,
            100% {
                opacity: 1
            }

            50% {
                opacity: .3
            }
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-family: var(--font-head);
            font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--white);
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -.03em;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem
        }

        .hero h1 .accent {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--amber), #fbbf24);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text
        }

        .hero-sub {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-mid);
            line-height: 1.8;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem
        }

        .hero-btns {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem
        }

        .btn-main {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--amber), var(--amber-deep));
            color: #000;
            padding: .85rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: .9rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all .3s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px var(--amber-glow-strong);
            border: 0;
            cursor: pointer
        }

        .btn-main:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 30px var(--amber-glow-strong)
        }

        .btn-ghost {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .5rem;
            background: 0;
            color: var(--text-light);
            padding: .85rem 1.8rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: .9rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            transition: all .3s;
            cursor: pointer
        }

        .btn-ghost:hover {
            border-color: var(--blue);
            color: var(--blue);
            background: var(--blue-glow)
        }

        .hero-stats {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2.5rem
        }

        .stat {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: .1rem
        }

        .stat-val {
            font-family: var(--font-head);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--white)
        }

        .stat-lbl {
            font-size: .7rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            letter-spacing: .06em;
            text-transform: uppercase
        }

        /* Hero Gauges Panel */
        .gauges-panel {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, .4);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .gauges-panel::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--blue), transparent);
            opacity: .4
        }

        .gp-head {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            padding-bottom: .8rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border)
        }

        .gp-title {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: .7rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: .1em
        }

        .gp-live {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .4rem;
            font-size: .65rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--green);
            padding: .2rem .6rem;
            background: var(--green-glow);
            border-radius: 100px
        }

        .gp-live .dot {
            width: 5px;
            height: 5px;
            background: var(--green);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: blink 1.5s infinite
        }

        .gauge-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem
        }

        .gauge {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem .5rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .01);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .04);
            border-radius: 12px
        }

        .gauge-circle {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto .6rem;
            position: relative
        }

        .gauge-circle svg {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            transform: rotate(-90deg)
        }

        .gauge-circle .track {
            fill: none;
            stroke: var(--border);
            stroke-width: 5
        }

        .gauge-circle .fill {
            fill: none;
            stroke-width: 5;
            stroke-linecap: round;
            stroke-dasharray: 220;
            stroke-dashoffset: 220;
            animation: gaugeFill 2s ease-out forwards
        }

        .gauge-circle .fill.blue {
            stroke: var(--blue)
        }

        .gauge-circle .fill.amber {
            stroke: var(--amber)
        }

        .gauge-circle .fill.green {
            stroke: var(--green)
        }

        .gauge-val {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: .85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--white)
        }

        @keyframes gaugeFill {
            to {
                stroke-dashoffset: var(--offset)
            }
        }

        .gauge-label {
            font-size: .65rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: .05em
        }

        .ticker {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .04);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: .6rem 1rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative
        }

        .ticker-inner {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            animation: scroll 20s linear infinite;
            white-space: nowrap
        }

        @keyframes scroll {
            0% {
                transform: translateX(0)
            }

            100% {
                transform: translateX(-50%)
            }
        }

        .ticker-item {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: .65rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .4rem;
            flex-shrink: 0
        }

        .ticker-item .up {
            color: var(--green)
        }

        .ticker-item .down {
            color: var(--red)
        }

        /* === BEFORE / AFTER === */
        .ba-section {
            padding: 6rem 0;
            position: relative
        }

        .ba-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border), transparent)
        }

        .ba-head {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3.5rem
        }

        .sec-tag {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: .7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: .15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--blue);
            margin-bottom: .8rem
        }

        .sec-title {
            font-family: var(--font-head);
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.6rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--white);
            line-height: 1.15;
            letter-spacing: -.02em;
            margin-bottom: .8rem
        }

        .sec-desc {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            max-width: 550px;
            margin: 0 auto
        }

        .ba-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 60px 1fr;
            gap: 0;
            align-items: stretch
        }

        .ba-col {
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.5rem
        }

        .ba-before {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(239, 68, 68, .04), rgba(239, 68, 68, .01));
            border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, .12)
        }

        .ba-after {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(34, 197, 94, .04), rgba(34, 197, 94, .01));
            border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, .12)
        }

        .ba-col-title {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: .7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: .12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: .3rem .8rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: inline-block;
            width: fit-content
        }

        .ba-before .ba-col-title {
            color: var(--red);
            background: var(--red-glow)
        }

        .ba-after .ba-col-title {
            color: var(--green);
            background: var(--green-glow)
        }

        .ba-item {
            display: flex;
            gap: .8rem;
            align-items: flex-start
        }

        .ba-icon {
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: .8rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: .1rem
        }

        .ba-before .ba-icon {
            background: var(--red-glow);
            color: var(--red)
        }

        .ba-after .ba-icon {
            background: var(--green-glow);
            color: var(--green)
        }

        .ba-item h4 {
            font-family: var(--font-head);
            font-size: .92rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-bright);
            margin-bottom: .2rem
        }

        .ba-item p {
            font-size: .82rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            line-height: 1.55
        }

        .ba-divider {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative
        }

        .ba-divider::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            width: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, var(--border), transparent)
        }

        .ba-arrow {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--amber);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--amber-glow)
        }

        /* === MODULES TABS === */
        .mod-section {
            padding: 6rem 0;
            background: var(--bg-deep);
            position: relative
        }

        .mod-section::before,
        .mod-section::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border), transparent)
        }

        .mod-section::before {
            top: 0
        }

        .mod-section::after {
            bottom: 0
        }

        .mod-head {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem
        }

        .mod-tabs {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: .5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap
        }

        .mod-tab {
            font-family: var(--font-head);
            font-size: .85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: .6rem 1.3rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text-dim);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all .3s
        }

        .mod-tab:hover {
            border-color: var(--blue);
            color: var(--text-light)
        }

        .mod-tab.active {
            background: var(--blue-glow);
            border-color: var(--blue);
            color: var(--blue);
            box-shadow: 0 0 16px var(--blue-glow)
        }

        .mod-panel {
            display: none;
            animation: fadeUp .4s ease
        }

        .mod-panel.active {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem
        }

        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(12px)
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0)
            }
        }

        .mod-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            transition: all .35s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .mod-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), var(--amber));
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity .3s
        }

        .mod-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--border-glow);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, .3)
        }

        .mod-card:hover::before {
            opacity: 1
        }

        .mod-card-num {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: .6rem;
            color: var(--border-glow);
            letter-spacing: .1em;
            margin-bottom: .6rem
        }

        .mod-card h3 {
            font-family: var(--font-head);
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-bright);
            margin-bottom: .4rem
        }

        .mod-card p {
            font-size: .8rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            line-height: 1.6
        }

        /* === PIPELINE === */
        .pipe-section {
            padding: 6rem 0;
            position: relative
        }

        .pipe-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border), transparent)
        }

        .pipe-head {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem
        }

        .pipeline {
            display: flex;
            align-items: stretch;
            gap: 0;
            position: relative;
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            overflow-x: auto;
            padding-bottom: 1rem
        }

        .pipeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 36px;
            left: 3%;
            right: 3%;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border-radius: 2px;
            z-index: 0
        }

        .pipeline::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 36px;
            left: 3%;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), var(--amber), var(--green));
            border-radius: 2px;
            animation: pipeFlow 3s ease-out forwards;
            width: 0;
            z-index: 1
        }

        @keyframes pipeFlow {
            to {
                width: 94%
            }
        }

        .pipe-step {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            padding: 0 .5rem;
            min-width: 130px
        }

        .pipe-node {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 3px solid var(--border);
            margin: 26px auto 1rem;
            transition: all .5s;
            position: relative
        }

        .pipe-step:hover .pipe-node {
            border-color: var(--amber);
            box-shadow: 0 0 16px var(--amber-glow-strong);
            background: var(--amber)
        }

        .pipe-step-num {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: .55rem;
            color: var(--blue);
            letter-spacing: .1em;
            margin-bottom: .3rem
        }

        .pipe-step h4 {
            font-family: var(--font-head);
            font-size: .88rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-bright);
            margin-bottom: .25rem
        }

        .pipe-step p {
            font-size: .68rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            line-height: 1.45
        }

        /* === METRICS === */
        .metrics-section {
            padding: 6rem 0;
            background: var(--bg-deep);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .metrics-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border), transparent)
        }

        .metrics-inner {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 5rem;
            align-items: center
        }

        .metric-cards {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1.2rem
        }

        .metric-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .02);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            transition: all .3s
        }

        .metric-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--border-glow);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(14, 165, 233, .06)
        }

        .metric-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--blue), transparent);
            opacity: .3
        }

        .metric-val {
            font-family: var(--font-head);
            font-size: 2.4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--white);
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: .3rem
        }

        .metric-val span {
            color: var(--amber)
        }

        .metric-lbl {
            font-size: .82rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            line-height: 1.45
        }

        .metric-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--border);
            border-radius: 2px;
            margin-top: .8rem;
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .metric-bar-fill {
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), var(--amber));
            width: 0;
            transition: width 1.5s ease-out
        }

        /* === DIFFERENTIATORS === */
        .diff-section {
            padding: 6rem 0;
            position: relative
        }

        .diff-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border), transparent)
        }

        .diff-head {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3.5rem
        }

        .diff-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 1.2rem
        }

        .diff-card {
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            transition: all .4s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .diff-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-glow), transparent);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity .3s
        }

        .diff-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            border-color: var(--border-glow);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, .3)
        }

        .diff-card:hover::before {
            opacity: 1
        }

        .diff-card>* {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1
        }

        .diff-ico {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: block
        }

        .diff-card h3 {
            font-family: var(--font-head);
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-bright);
            margin-bottom: .5rem
        }

        .diff-card p {
            font-size: .85rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            line-height: 1.6
        }

        /* === TECH STRIP === */
        .tech-strip {
            padding: 4rem 0;
            background: var(--bg-deep);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border)
        }

        .tech-inner {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap
        }

        .tech-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .8rem
        }

        .tech-ico {
            width: 42px;
            height: 42px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .02)
        }

        .tech-txt h4 {
            font-size: .85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-light)
        }

        .tech-txt p {
            font-size: .7rem;
            color: var(--text-dim)
        }

        /* === CTA === */
        .cta {
            padding: 7rem 0;
            position: relative;
            text-align: center;
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .cta::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--blue-glow) 0%, transparent 60%);
            border-radius: 50%
        }

        .cta .sec-title {
            max-width: 650px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto
        }

        .cta-sub {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            max-width: 480px;
            margin: .8rem auto 2.5rem
        }

        .cta-btns {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap
        }

        .cta-trust {
            font-size: .72rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap
        }

        .cta-trust span {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .3rem
        }

        /* === FOOTER === */
        .footer {
            padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border)
        }

        .footer-inner {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center
        }

        .footer-left p {
            font-size: .75rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            margin-top: .6rem
        }

        .footer-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem
        }

        .footer-links a {
            font-size: .78rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color .3s
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: var(--blue)
        }

        .built-by {
            font-size: .68rem;
            color: var(--border-glow);
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding-top: 1.2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .03)
        }

        .built-by a {
            color: var(--amber-deep);
            text-decoration: none
        }

        .built-by a:hover {
            color: var(--amber)
        }

        /* === REVEAL === */
        .rv {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(24px);
            transition: all .6s cubic-bezier(.16, 1, .3, 1)
        }

        .rv.vis {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0)
        }

        /* === RESPONSIVE === */
        @media(max-width:1024px) {
            .hero .ctn {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                text-align: center
            }

            .hero-sub {
                margin-left: auto;
                margin-right: auto
            }

            .hero-btns {
                justify-content: center
            }

            .hero-stats {
                justify-content: center
            }

            .gauges-panel {
                display: none
            }

            .ba-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 1.5rem
            }

            .ba-divider {
                display: none
            }

            .metrics-inner {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 3rem
            }

            .diff-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr)
            }
        }

        @media(max-width:768px) {
            .nav-links {
                display: none
            }

            .mob-tog {
                display: block
            }

            .nav-links.open {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                position: absolute;
                top: 100%;
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
                background: rgba(6, 9, 15, .98);
                backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
                padding: 1.5rem;
                gap: 1.2rem;
                border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border)
            }

            .diff-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr
            }

            .mod-panel.active {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr
            }

            .pipeline {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1rem
            }

            .pipeline::before,
            .pipeline::after {
                display: none
            }

            .pipe-step {
                text-align: left;
                display: flex;
                gap: 1rem;
                align-items: flex-start;
                padding: 0
            }

            .pipe-node {
                margin: 0;
                flex-shrink: 0
            }

            .metric-cards {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr
            }

            .tech-inner {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 1.2rem
            }

            .footer-inner {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1.2rem;
                text-align: center
            }

            .cta-btns {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center
            }

            .hero-btns {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center
            }

            .hero-stats {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                gap: 1.5rem
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- ===== NAV ===== -->
    <nav class="nav" id="mainNav">
        <div class="ctn">
            <a href="#" class="logo">
                <div class="logo-mark">Ez</div>
                <div class="logo-name">EzFMC<span>.</span></div>
            </a>
            <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
                <li><a href="#problem">Pain Points</a></li>
                <li><a href="#modules">Modules</a></li>
                <li><a href="#lifecycle">Lifecycle</a></li>
                <li><a href="#impact">Impact</a></li>
                <li><a href="#edge">Why EzFMC</a></li>
                <li><a href="#cta" class="btn-cta">Request Demo</a></li>
            </ul>
            <button class="mob-tog" id="mobTog" aria-label="Menu"><span></span><span></span><span></span></button>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-glow"></div>
        <div class="hero-glow2"></div>
        <div class="ctn">
            <div>
                <div class="hero-badge"><span class="dot"></span> Built for Ghana's OMCs</div>
                <h1>Every Litre.<br>Every Station.<br><span class="accent">Total Command.</span></h1>
                <p class="hero-sub">From BDC procurement to the pump, from NPA compliance to your financial statements —
                    EzFMC is the unified command centre that gives Oil Marketing Companies complete control over every
                    operation, every cedi, and every regulatory obligation.</p>
                <div class="hero-btns">
                    <a href="#cta" class="btn-main">Request a Demo →</a>
                    <a href="#modules" class="btn-ghost">Explore Modules</a>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-stats">
                    <div class="stat">
                        <div class="stat-val">16</div>
                        <div class="stat-lbl">Core Modules</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <div class="stat-val">25+</div>
                        <div class="stat-lbl">NPA Components</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <div class="stat-val">100%</div>
                        <div class="stat-lbl">UPPF Automation</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="gauges-panel">
                <div class="gp-head">
                    <div class="gp-title">EzFMC Command Centre</div>
                    <div class="gp-live"><span class="dot"></span> Live</div>
                </div>
                <div class="gauge-row">
                    <div class="gauge">
                        <div class="gauge-circle">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 80 80">
                                <circle class="track" cx="40" cy="40" r="35" />
                                <circle class="fill blue" cx="40" cy="40" r="35" style="--offset:55" />
                            </svg>
                            <div class="gauge-val">GH₵ 4.2M</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="gauge-label">Revenue MTD</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gauge">
                        <div class="gauge-circle">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 80 80">
                                <circle class="track" cx="40" cy="40" r="35" />
                                <circle class="fill amber" cx="40" cy="40" r="35" style="--offset:88" />
                            </svg>
                            <div class="gauge-val">318K L</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="gauge-label">Litres Sold</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gauge">
                        <div class="gauge-circle">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 80 80">
                                <circle class="track" cx="40" cy="40" r="35" />
                                <circle class="fill green" cx="40" cy="40" r="35" style="--offset:22" />
                            </svg>
                            <div class="gauge-val">GH₵ 89K</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="gauge-label">UPPF Claims</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="ticker">
                    <div class="ticker-inner">
                        <div class="ticker-item">⛽ Spintex PMS <span class="up">↑ 12.7%</span></div>
                        <div class="ticker-item">⛽ Kasoa AGO <span class="up">↑ 8.1%</span></div>
                        <div class="ticker-item">📋 UPPF Jan Filed <span class="up">✓</span></div>
                        <div class="ticker-item">🔔 EPA Cert expires in 14d</div>
                        <div class="ticker-item">💰 Dealer Bal GH₵ 265K</div>
                        <div class="ticker-item">📊 Variance 0.3% <span class="up">✓</span></div>
                        <div class="ticker-item">⛽ Spintex PMS <span class="up">↑ 12.7%</span></div>
                        <div class="ticker-item">⛽ Kasoa AGO <span class="up">↑ 8.1%</span></div>
                        <div class="ticker-item">📋 UPPF Jan Filed <span class="up">✓</span></div>
                        <div class="ticker-item">🔔 EPA Cert expires in 14d</div>
                        <div class="ticker-item">💰 Dealer Bal GH₵ 265K</div>
                        <div class="ticker-item">📊 Variance 0.3% <span class="up">✓</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== BEFORE / AFTER ===== -->
    <section class="ba-section" id="problem">
        <div class="ctn">
            <div class="ba-head rv">
                <div class="sec-tag">The Problem → The Solution</div>
                <h2 class="sec-title">From chaos to command.</h2>
                <p class="sec-desc">Ghana's OMCs lose millions each year to fragmented tools and manual compliance.
                    Here's how EzFMC changes everything.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ba-grid rv">
                <div class="ba-col ba-before">
                    <div class="ba-col-title">✕ Without EzFMC</div>
                    <div class="ba-item">
                        <div class="ba-icon">🔀</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>Fragmented Systems</h4>
                            <p>Spreadsheets, WhatsApp, separate accounting software. Nothing connected.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ba-item">
                        <div class="ba-icon">📋</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>NPA Compliance Chaos</h4>
                            <p>25+ pricing components tracked manually. Missed deadlines, penalties.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ba-item">
                        <div class="ba-icon">💸</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>Cash Flow Blindness</h4>
                            <p>No real-time view of station revenue, dealer balances, or true margins.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ba-item">
                        <div class="ba-icon">⛽</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>Inventory Black Holes</h4>
                            <p>Tank dip discrepancies and unreconciled deliveries. Variance is invisible.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ba-item">
                        <div class="ba-icon">🧮</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>Manual UPPF Claims</h4>
                            <p>Monthly Excel calculations. Freight zone lookups by hand. Hours of error-prone work.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ba-item">
                        <div class="ba-icon">📊</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>No Strategic Visibility</h4>
                            <p>COCO, DODO, CODO: each a silo. Decision-making is reactive.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="ba-divider">
                    <div class="ba-arrow">→</div>
                </div>
                <div class="ba-col ba-after">
                    <div class="ba-col-title">✓ With EzFMC</div>
                    <div class="ba-item">
                        <div class="ba-icon">🔗</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>Unified Platform</h4>
                            <p>One system: procurement, stations, finance, compliance, HR, AI. All connected.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ba-item">
                        <div class="ba-icon">⚡</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>Instant NPA Updates</h4>
                            <p>One entry updates all 25+ components, every station, every price. Automatic.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ba-item">
                        <div class="ba-icon">📈</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>Real-Time Financials</h4>
                            <p>Live GL posting, station-level P&L, aging reports, dealer credit at a glance.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ba-item">
                        <div class="ba-icon">🎯</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>Precision Inventory</h4>
                            <p>GRV ↔ tank ↔ session linked. Temperature-corrected. WAC costed. Zero guesswork.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ba-item">
                        <div class="ba-icon">🤖</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>Auto UPPF Filing</h4>
                            <p>NPA distance matrix built in. Calculations instant. 22.5% deductions handled.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ba-item">
                        <div class="ba-icon">🗺️</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>Portfolio Command</h4>
                            <p>All models, all stations, one dashboard. AI-powered insights on demand.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== MODULES (TABBED) ===== -->
    <section class="mod-section" id="modules">
        <div class="ctn">
            <div class="mod-head rv">
                <div class="sec-tag">Core Modules</div>
                <h2 class="sec-title">16 modules. One platform.<br>Zero excuses.</h2>
                <p class="sec-desc">Purpose-built for how OMCs actually operate — not how generic ERPs think you should.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mod-tabs rv" id="modTabs">
                <button class="mod-tab active" data-tab="ops">⛽ Operations</button>
                <button class="mod-tab" data-tab="fin">💰 Finance</button>
                <button class="mod-tab" data-tab="comp">📋 Compliance</button>
                <button class="mod-tab" data-tab="intel">🤖 Intelligence</button>
            </div>
            <div id="panel-ops" class="mod-panel active">
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">01</div>
                    <h3>Procurement & Purchase Orders</h3>
                    <p>BDC ordering, multi-product POs, credit checks, approval workflows, automatic NPA pricing.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">02</div>
                    <h3>Dispatch & Logistics</h3>
                    <p>Transporter assignment, vehicle & driver tracking, compartment loading, waybill generation,
                        seals.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">03</div>
                    <h3>Station Operations</h3>
                    <p>Tank dip recording, delivery receiving (GRV), variance tracking, station expenses with approvals.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">04</div>
                    <h3>Pump & Session Management</h3>
                    <p>Shift open/close, meter readings, attendant assignment, cash reconciliation, electronic journal.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">05</div>
                    <h3>Tank & Inventory</h3>
                    <p>Real-time tank levels, temperature-corrected volumes, WAC costing, stock transfers, perpetual
                        inventory.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">06</div>
                    <h3>Mart & C-Store</h3>
                    <p>Non-fuel retail management, POS integration, mart inventory, pricing control, sales tracking.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="panel-fin" class="mod-panel">
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">07</div>
                    <h3>Finance & Accounting</h3>
                    <p>Segmented chart of accounts, journal entries, trial balance, income statement, balance sheet,
                        cash flow.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">08</div>
                    <h3>AP/AR & Banking</h3>
                    <p>Vendor invoices, customer receipts, dealer credit, aging reports, bank reconciliation,
                        multi-currency.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">09</div>
                    <h3>HR & Payroll</h3>
                    <p>Employee management, SSNIT/Tier 2/3, PAYE, leave management, performance reviews, payslips.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">10</div>
                    <h3>Fixed Assets</h3>
                    <p>Asset register, depreciation schedules, transfers, disposals, lifecycle tracking for
                        infrastructure.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">11</div>
                    <h3>Sales & CRM</h3>
                    <p>Lead pipeline, corporate sales, quote management, delivery scheduling, collections tracking.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="panel-comp" class="mod-panel">
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">12</div>
                    <h3>NPA Pricing Engine</h3>
                    <p>25+ price components modeled. Price windows with effective dates. Automatic ex-depot, dealer, and
                        pump price calculations.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">13</div>
                    <h3>UPPF & Freight Claims</h3>
                    <p>NPA-approved distance matrix, automatic UPPF calculations, 22.5% tanker owner deductions,
                        transporter claims.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">14</div>
                    <h3>Compliance & Certification</h3>
                    <p>EPA permits, fire certificates, pump calibrations, expiry alerts, compliance dashboard,
                        audit-ready trails.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">15</div>
                    <h3>Internal Audit</h3>
                    <p>Audit planning, finding documentation, corrective actions, 5C framework, automated gap detection.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="panel-intel" class="mod-panel">
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">16</div>
                    <h3>EzPilot AI Assistant</h3>
                    <p>Ask in plain English: "What was total sales at Spintex last week?" Instant answers across all 16
                        modules. Your AI co-pilot.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">—</div>
                    <h3>Anomaly Detection</h3>
                    <p>System flags unusual patterns — variance spikes, revenue drops, compliance gaps — before they
                        become problems.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mod-card">
                    <div class="mod-card-num">—</div>
                    <h3>Demand Forecasting</h3>
                    <p>Predictive analytics for fuel demand, inventory planning, and cash flow projection across all
                        stations.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== PIPELINE LIFECYCLE ===== -->
    <section class="pipe-section" id="lifecycle">
